+------------------+
Difference: cover vs contain
cover	contain
Fills the entire container	Fits the entire image inside the container
May crop the image	Never crops the image
Usually used for hero banners	Used when the whole image must be visible
5. background-position

Controls where the background image appears.

Center
background-position:center;
